## Final architecture (locked, IPI-695 ADR)

```text
Brand Hub
   ↓
Supabase start-brand-crawl Edge Function
   ↓
Atomic Supabase quota RPC — IPI-693 (Firecrawl cost control)
   ↓
Firecrawl website crawl
   ↓
Supabase firecrawl-webhook
   ↓
Supabase brand-intelligence Edge Function
   ↓
Cloudflare AI Gateway REST — IPI-697 / IPI-699
   ↓
Cloudflare Workers AI (@cf/...)
```

| Cost surface | Owner | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Firecrawl (pages, concurrency) | **IPI-693** | Atomic Supabase RPC before crawl |
| Workers AI / LLM inference | **IPI-460** (managed Gateway spend limits) | 5 metadata fields: `organization_id`, `brand_id`, `environment`, `feature`, `request_type` |
| Custom Cloudflare Worker | Not required for Phase A | IPI-455 parked |

