## Hard rules (do not break)

- **Never** `supabase start` for schema truth (remote-only policy)
- **Never** `supabase migration repair` (no squash / rewrite / renumber)
- **Never** `--prune` Edge Functions
- **Never** report `RLS enabled + zero policies = weak RLS` without checking whether default-deny is intentional
- **Never** use Cloudflare AI Gateway spend limits as a Firecrawl cost control (separate quotas — see IPI-693)
- **Never** mark Done from a branch name or local-only change (require merged code + live verification + green CI)
- **Always** use full task names: `IPI-NNN · SPEC — Title`

